		</div>

						<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">위키백과, 우리 모두의 백과사전.</div>
					</div>
					<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-content-subtitle"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(<a href="/w/index.php?title=%EB%82%9C%EC%88%98%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%EA%B8%B0&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="난수발생기">난수발생기</a>에서 넘어옴)</span></div></div>
					
					
					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="ko" dir="ltr" data-mw-parsoid-version="0.23.0.0-alpha27" data-mw-html-version="2.8.0"><section data-mw-section-id="0" id="mwAQ"><figure class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Thumb" id="mwAg"><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/파일:Two_red_dice_01.svg" class="mw-file-description" id="mwAw"><img resource="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/파일:Two_red_dice_01.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/36/Two_red_dice_01.svg/250px-Two_red_dice_01.svg.png" decoding="async" data-file-width="671" data-file-height="430" data-file-type="drawing" height="160" width="250" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/36/Two_red_dice_01.svg/500px-Two_red_dice_01.svg.png 2x" class="mw-file-element" id="mwBA"></a><figcaption id="mwBQ"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/주사위" title="주사위" id="mwBg">주사위</a>는 기계식 하드웨어 난수 발생기의 한 예이다.</figcaption></figure>

<p id="mwBw"><b id="mwCA">난수 발생기</b>(亂數發生機, <span style="font-size: smaller;" about="#mwt1" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw="{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;llang&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./틀:Llang&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;en&quot;},&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;random number generator, '''RNG'''&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}" id="mwCQ"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/영어" title="영어">영어</a><span typeof="mw:Entity">:</span> </span><span lang="en" about="#mwt1">random number generator, <b>RNG</b></span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./분류:영어_표기를_포함한_문서#난수%20발생기" about="#mwt1" id="mwCg">) 또는 <b id="mwCw">난수 생성기</b>(亂數生成機)는 <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/무작위성" title="무작위성" id="mwDA">무작위성</a> 기회보다 이론적으로 예측을 더 할 수 없도록 일련의 숫자나 심볼을 생성하는 장치이다. 난수발생기는 진정한 난수를 생성하는 진정한 <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/하드웨어_난수발생기" title="하드웨어 난수발생기" class="mw-redirect" id="mwDQ">하드웨어 난수발생기</a>(HRNG) 또는 무작위의 숫자를 생성하지만 실제로 결정적이면서 PRNG의 상태를 모르는 경우 재현이 가능한 <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/유사난수_발생기" title="유사난수 발생기" class="mw-redirect" id="mwDg">유사난수 발생기</a>(PRNG)일 수 있다.</p>

</section><section data-mw-section-id="1" id="mwDw" aria-labelledby="같이_보기"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="같이_보기"><span id=".EA.B0.99.EC.9D.B4_.EB.B3.B4.EA.B8.B0" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>같이 보기</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%EB%82%9C%EC%88%98_%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%EA%B8%B0&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="부분 편집: 같이 보기"><span>편집</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<ul id="mwEA"><li id="mwEQ"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/확률적_알고리즘" title="확률적 알고리즘" id="mwEg">확률적 알고리즘</a></li>
<li id="mwEw"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/확률_변수" title="확률 변수" id="mwFA">확률 변수</a></li>
<li id="mwFQ"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/무작위성" title="무작위성" id="mwFg">무작위성</a></li></ul>

</section><section data-mw-section-id="2" id="mwFw" aria-labelledby="외부_링크"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="외부_링크"><span id=".EC.99.B8.EB.B6.80_.EB.A7.81.ED.81.AC" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>외부 링크</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%EB%82%9C%EC%88%98_%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%EA%B8%B0&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="부분 편집: 외부 링크"><span>편집</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<ul id="mwGA"><li id="mwGQ"><a rel="mw:ExtLink nofollow" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200605104447/https://www.random.org/" class="external text" id="mwGg">RANDOM.ORG</a> True Random Number Service</li>
<li id="mwGw"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw="{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;웹 인용&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./틀:웹_인용&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;last&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Clewett&quot;},&quot;first&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;James&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Random Numbers&quot;},&quot;url&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;http://www.numberphile.com/videos/random_numbers.html&quot;},&quot;work&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Numberphile&quot;},&quot;publisher&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;[[:en:Brady Haran]]&quot;},&quot;확인날짜&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;2019-09-05&quot;},&quot;보존url&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20160319140933/http://www.numberphile.com/videos/random_numbers.html&quot;},&quot;보존날짜&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;2016-03-19&quot;},&quot;url-status&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;dead&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}" id="mwHA">Clewett, James. <a rel="mw:ExtLink nofollow" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20160319140933/http://www.numberphile.com/videos/random_numbers.html" class="external text"><span typeof="mw:Entity">“</span>Random Numbers<span typeof="mw:Entity">”</span></a>. <span typeof="mw:Entity">《</span>Numberphile<span typeof="mw:Entity">》</span>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink/Interwiki" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brady%20Haran" title="en:Brady Haran" class="extiw">en:Brady Haran</a>. 2016년 3월 19일에 <a rel="mw:ExtLink nofollow" href="http://www.numberphile.com/videos/random_numbers.html" class="external text">원본 문서</a>에서 보존된 문서<span class="reference-accessdate">. 2019년 9월 5일에 확인함</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Numberphile&amp;rft.atitle=Random+Numbers&amp;rft.aulast=Clewett&amp;rft.aufirst=James&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.numberphile.com%2Fvideos%2Frandom_numbers.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fko.wikipedia.org%3A%EB%82%9C%EC%88%98+%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%EA%B8%B0" class="Z3988" about="#mwt2" id="mwHQ"><span style="display:none;"><span typeof="mw:Entity">&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="mwHg"><a rel="mw:ExtLink nofollow" href="https://sites.google.com/site/simulationarchitecture/jrand" class="external text" id="mwHw">jRand</a> <a rel="mw:ExtLink nofollow" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20170401085719/https://sites.google.com/site/simulationarchitecture/jrand" about="#mwt3" typeof="mw:Transclusion" class="external text" data-mw="{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;웹아카이브&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./틀:웹아카이브&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20170401085719/https://sites.google.com/site/simulationarchitecture/jrand&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}" id="mwIA">보관됨</a><span about="#mwt3"> 2017-04-01 - </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/웨이백_머신" title="웨이백 머신" about="#mwt3">웨이백 머신</a><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./분류:웹아카이브_틀_웨이백_링크" about="#mwt3" id="mwIQ"> a Java-based framework for the generation of simulation sequences, including pseudo-random sequences of numbers</li>
